com.camerontec.util.datamodel.expression

Interface ExpressionEvaluationTarget

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractExpressionEvaluationTarget

    public interface ExpressionEvaluationTarget
    Instances of this interface are used as targets for expression evaluations.
